{"tid":680944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【腐液淋妻】近月婚姻亮紅燈 狠夫：愛不會再重來！","createTime":"2018-05-27T14:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T04:11:53.000Z","uid":29627,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"38c4056eb124210933f26b239cf9e31881546ef2","tid":680944,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"【腐液淋妻】近月婚姻亮紅燈 狠夫：愛不會再重來！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527420498_aec7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527420498_aec7.jpg&h=cad56ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527420620_ad98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527420620_ad98.jpg&h=a6f681de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑犯更在微信的個性簽名上寫着：「愛不會再重來」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527420619_82bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527420619_82bf.jpg&h=5a50851c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑犯在月初上載一張戴黑超的相片到fb，而他今日送院檢查時亦戴黑超。<br />\n<br />\n 尖沙嘴一海鮮酒家發生淋潑腐液傷人案，一名40歲打扮新潮的男子，懷疑任知客的太太紅杏出牆，今晨在太太工作的地方向對方淋通渠水，令她臉部及眼嚴重受傷。據知，二人同為40歲，結婚20年，育有兩名分別12及16歲的女兒，惟近月二人婚姻出現問題，女事主搬離荃灣區的寓所後，到酒樓任職知客養家。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，疑犯任職地盤，平日打扮新潮，外表看上只有20多歲，從他上載到fb的自拍照中可見，他經常穿著窄身牛仔褲，頸纏圍巾，有時更戴黑超示人，有親友當時留言笑稱：「像黑色老大」「酷」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》發現，疑犯與妻子在fb上的互動甚少，而且疑犯更在微信的個性簽名上寫着：「愛不會再重來」，似乎對這段婚姻感到失望。記者曾到疑兇位於荃灣的住所了解，發現上址單位分間作兩間劏房，疑兇的住所無人應門。鄰居余女士指，事主夫婦打扮新潮，何妻外表「幾靚」，兩人的女兒分別於區內就讀中學及小學，大女成績不俗，更會負責買餸煮飯，男事主平日亦會送女兒上學。街坊董太則指，男事主早出晚歸，女事主則約中午出門，晚上才下班回家，偶爾穿著酒樓制服，亦未曾聽過事主單位傳出爭執聲，董太形容事主一家都斯文有禮，但半年前開始沒有見到女事主出現，對於今次事件感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180527/58244710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F58244710&d=FFCZ1dYqrAUht%2BKZNxHPP57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=de883346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F58244710&h=3c6acb41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180527/58244710</a>"},{"pid":"8e2204c39927f85c5fe07673751807133588d89f","tid":680944,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"呢單野發生咗成日，而家先見有post!<br />\n<br />\n狼咗d,帽事變刑事，昂鳩鳩咗就坐十年八年，<br />\n兇手果樣睇開d都有Mk妹食下啦，使唔使咗淋個老婆通渠水呀"},{"pid":"7d17c6db6ba1f36f366e5b27b3a074a337b6ca88","tid":680944,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"兩條友四張嘢仲咁潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d17c005aef4780a2fc9a513518f22858c346f3","tid":680944,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:26:35.000Z","msg":"潑酸去人地塊面真係狠毒到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5612a8f493c3be77527bef27c69ddc365a550291","tid":680944,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"睇上去Milf，可以一戰"},{"pid":"79727d17227b942ebf15e549e8ce6a357b0e89da","tid":680944,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:34:58.000Z","msg":"留名排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce797b9cb23216fe3b6dae3f1f07ff0050ebf6f3","tid":680944,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"個男人啲皮膚好嫰, 似20歲多啲"},{"pid":"4a90b7117740784d293e2686c815b69caea56f97","tid":680944,"uid":7814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"打撚曬格睇條毛"},{"pid":"155d3133b3e6b377c28f50c3790adda90580f257","tid":680944,"uid":51509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0